         MACRO                                                             @CALL
&NAME    @CALL &ROUTINE,&ENTRY=0                                           @CALL
.*********************************************************************     @CALL
.*         MACRO IS USED TO CALL SUBROUTINES                         *     @CALL
.*********************************************************************     @CALL
&NAME    LA    R1,&ENTRY                                                   @CALL
         L     R15,@&ROUTINE                                               @CALL
         BALR  R14,R15                                                     @CALL
.*********************************************************************     @CALL
           MEND                                                            @CALL
